{"tid":1857082,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣激罕晒半裸噴血浴照","createTime":"2020-02-02T04:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T06:43:06.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e1b7895e0f973fb02616ba0dce1c18a8fe2307","tid":1857082,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"「大美人」李嘉欣今年農曆新年就同咗老公許晉亨及仔仔許建彤（Jayden）去咗北海道滑雪，佢喺社交網大晒全家福，仲見到8歲嘅Jayden已經大個仔，身高同嘉欣只相差一個頭，而老公更攬實Jayden，溫馨爆燈～<br />\n不過除咗見憤見熟嘅一家三口滑雪相，李嘉欣仲偷偷喺限時動態派福利，貼出一張着上浴袍面向雪景嘅激罕大露背相，見佢浴袍跌到落雙膊，玉背見人，似乎係準備浸溫泉，呢下忽然派糧又真係估你唔到啵！"},{"pid":"062dc8557eed38fd42dfb3789ac0eca3d9c2775a","tid":1857082,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200201/photo/bkn-20200201114923349-0201_00862_001_05p.jpg?20200201140955\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200201114923349-0201_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20200201140955&h=dfea7a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6768e24f6b79745691e8339fa7f36001a6a499a","tid":1857082,"uid":99962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17e5105d5fd6656203d9d41f557d19350aaa3c6c","tid":1857082,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200201/photo/bkn-20200201114923349-0201_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200201140955\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200201114923349-0201_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200201140955&h=6fd7283e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200201/photo/bkn-20200201114923349-0201_00862_001_04p.jpg?20200201140955\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200201%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200201114923349-0201_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20200201140955&h=5ecf1f49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e526c1b6dcafe847a0cd938b1765f1de849274d1","tid":1857082,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6dOPfhA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6dOPfhA.gif&h=450eea07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27a42219ada6ca29ca5d718dc5d38a929e1184be","tid":1857082,"uid":313750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:29:15.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係宇宙第一大美人開post"},{"pid":"b3df7cd843ba4137dc0d8ec87ea08d0a6f40a81c","tid":1857082,"uid":171849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"佢上次去滑雪係咪滯留左係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次怕唔怕又中多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adccf1b16177a259d211c1028277186fa1379f7","tid":1857082,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27a42219ada6ca29ca5d718dc5d38a929e1184be","tid":1857082,"uid":313750,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:29:15.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係宇宙第一大美人開post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:37:29.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96b464e6da877b786476b0c0850923c0049fa39","tid":1857082,"uid":29816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a28d1701f8996adc062236e76708379ab89346","tid":1857082,"uid":313514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:39:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef7fa976a65c7058117065bf64cfecb859b50aa4","tid":1857082,"uid":222155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"唔知佢今次係咪仲係搭CX呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>大風雪滯北海道3日　李嘉欣鬧國泰安排混亂</strong></span><br />\n2016年12月25日(日) 12:28   <br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣一家人因受大風雪影響，滯留日本三日，她鬧爆國泰安排失當。(高嘉業攝/李嘉欣微博圖片)<br />\n李嘉欣一家人因受大風雪影響，滯留日本三日，她鬧爆國泰安排失當。(高嘉業攝/李嘉欣微博圖片)<br />\n<br />\n日本北海道大風雪令航班延誤，不少港人滯留當地的新千歲機場。大美人李嘉欣(Michele)趁住聖誕節同老公許晉亨及囝囝，去了北海道過一個白色聖誕，原本是一件開心事，奈何回程時遇到大風雪要滯留，加上國泰航空公司安排失當，令Michele足足滯留當地三日，由上周四(22日)開始等機位，每次被航空公司通知去check in，最後都失望而回，她更以「難民營」來形容新千歲機場的情況。令Michele最氣憤的是其他航空公司的乘客都已順利離開，Michele於是忍不住在微博開火：「我們在千歲機場等了3天，沒通知和安排，其他航空公司都飛了。」 <br />\n<br />\n仍然滯留日本的Michele，今日接受東網電話訪問，直言一家人從未試過如此辛苦：「我哋今朝凌晨4點先離開機場，要搵車搵酒店，仲要係零下廿幾度，真係未試過咁辛苦嘅經歷。搞咗前後4日，國泰嘅安排真係非常之唔好，情況非常之混亂！」Michele表示，理解首兩日(22日及23日)天氣不穩要停航，但之後兩日即使天氣好轉，仍未能獲安排返港：「呢兩日都仲係好混亂，機場都好多小朋友，好多BB，大家都苦不堪言！」嬲爆的Michele怒轟國泰：「其他航空公司都已經飛咗，國泰依然冇提供食宿、冇安排！」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161225/mobile/bkn-20161225122842591-1225_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161225%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161225122842591-1225_00822_001.html&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9K%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=0de964d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161225/mobile/bkn-20161225122842591-1225_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9e60dec065634341f69214c2a37458edd948bb88","tid":1857082,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"兩粒黑的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4145fa78cfb556458e5e5cb0bbde672e8ec36381","tid":1857082,"uid":141376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e60dec065634341f69214c2a37458edd948bb88","tid":1857082,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:07:06.000Z","msg":"兩粒黑的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:43:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，笑撚到我出煙#"}]}